# Make Private key
```
openssl genrsa -out private_key.pem 2048
```

# Make Public key
```
openssl rsa -in private_key.pem -outform PEM -pubout -out ROZP_13981909_01.pem
```


# Sign File by public key

## Signing:
```
openssl dgst -sha256 -sign private_key.pem -out ROZP_13980919_01.json.sign ROZP_13980919_01.json
```

## Verifying just the signature:
```
openssl dgst -sha256 -verify ROZP_13981909_01.pem -signature ROZP_13980919_01.json.sign ROZP_13980919_01.json
```

